@BizomWebAPI @OnlineInvoicesManagement @GetRequestLogs @WorkflowAutomation @Innovation
Feature: Get Request Logs API Testing for Online Invoices
  As a system user
  I want to test the get request logs endpoint for online invoices
  So that I can ensure proper functionality and data retrieval for online invoices request logs management

  Background:
    Given I set up base URI for transactions
    When I set up request specification
      |HeaderName|HeaderValue|
      |Content-Type|application/json|
      |Accept|*/*|
      |Accept-Encoding|gzip,deflate, br|
      |Connection|keep-alive|

  @Negative @Security
  Scenario: TC_01 Get request logs without access token
    When I send the GET request to "onlineinvoices_getrequestlogs" endpoint
    Then I should see the response code as "200"
    And the HTML response should contain page title "Users"
    And verify response time is less than "2500" milliseconds

